Burt Flickinger, managing director 
of Strategic Resource Group, talks about retail sales and 
 consumer spending  during the holiday season.  Flickinger, speaking with Sara Eisen and Scarlet Fu on 
Bloomberg Television's "InsideTrack," also discusses Sears 
Holdings Corp.'s plan to close 100 to 120 Kmart and Sears 
full-line stores. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 04:22
 